{"tid":964501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為用iPhone Tweet慶祝新年　急刪仍遭截圖廣傳","createTime":"2019-01-01T10:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T16:38:06.000Z","uid":41404,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d2846f120dc68290aea6157227e83998de3840","tid":964501,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:57:53.000Z","msg":"迎來新的一年，各大廠商紛紛在社交媒體發文慶祝。不過上年走在風口浪尖的華為卻一不留神，為競爭對手做了宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n華為科技昨天（12月31日）在Twitter發布新年祝福，祝大家2019年快樂，不過貼文顯示是用蘋果iPhone手機發出。華為發現這一疏漏後，立即將貼文刪除，但仍然被一名網絡紅人Marques Brownlee截圖捕獲，引來大批網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2273146/org/f13d997fee36facee57d52661b007b15.jpg/pmpM6pIHIHEFnWYMvkbecrYD4Xb502c4Sa3epkmt3qY?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2273146%2Forg%2Ff13d997fee36facee57d52661b007b15.jpg%2FpmpM6pIHIHEFnWYMvkbecrYD4Xb502c4Sa3epkmt3qY%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=24e61508&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dfa6e94ccefb47ecc0a543b8894b74d13a0b19a","tid":964501,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"笑甚麼，iPhone都是華為的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ba1987d4dd1829af5504ed88dc73b3197d3511","tid":964501,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"口裏說不<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358141702325133ad78efcf6d5bfd3540d5439e5","tid":964501,"uid":42153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e0a653235be8cdf83b0bc005757c8ba640efee","tid":964501,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T11:01:07.000Z","msg":"身體很誠實"},{"pid":"3ce364a9cdfd88e2c20b070574ec811805dda9d5","tid":964501,"uid":10197,"like":0,"dis